hackathon-rules: All entrants should have registered through hackcmu.com

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: ASUS Monitor (worth $280) and Razer Deathadder Mouse (worth $30) for each team member
Amazon Echo (worth $180) for each team member
One Leap Motion Controller (worth $75) per team member
Oculus Rift Dev Kits (worth $350) for the best python project per team member for the best use of python
Apple Watches (worth $350) per team member for the best use of eBay's API or data
$100 Amazon gift card per person and entry to Dave and Busters with GoDaddy for the best use of GoDaddy's API and/or domain names
Rosewill Keyboard (worth $100) per team member for the most amusing project
Microsoft Band (worth $140) per team member for the best use of Microsoft APIs
Gift Cards for every member of the winning team

hackathon-description-header: Create anything you'd like at HackCMU 2015!
